Helicopter: @tomanderson22 @joshanderson193

MB01YIQCS5FCFAB

Repost via: @alpinestars_racing_aus

node.text:
See what it takes to make 2 custom @motogp suits for @garrettgerloff at our production racing facility in Italy and then transport the suits to Holland on time for FP1! 

This valiant effort takes the focused talents of over 20 skilled staff members to make this happen, all sewn by hand utilizing Alpinestars top protection materials and technology. 

ONE GOAL ONE VISION ONE TEAM 

#AlpinestarsProtects #OneGoalOneVision #ThinkingAhead #RacingAhead

node.title: Follow The Journey! Behind the scenes at Alpinestars.

Feature Friday on @motoamerica / Alpinestars rider @jakegagne. 

Jake has won 1️⃣3️⃣ consecutive races this season! 

Jake had 11 podiums in 2020 and a little fact on Jake: He qualified for and raced in the 2015 @promotocross races in Utah and nearly finished in the top twenty.

Are you seeing RED too!? 😎

Alpinestsrs “Meta Road Shoes” 

Astars Quick Facts:

Designed for mechanics and teams looking for good all-day comfort and occasional road running. 

Easy to slip on design with large toebox that allows the toes to spread when kneeling for greater levels of comfort. 

EVA insert located in main midsole beneath the heel provides long lasting softness. 

Midsole wall wrapping snugly secures the foot and provides good stability and comfort. 

Oil resistant rubber sole improves grip on dirty surfaces. 

4 colors available.

$139.95 US Dollars

#AlpinestarsCasual #Alpinestars #TeamWear

node.text:
The best just got better. 🏁

The all-new, refined Supertech R boot. 

Astars quick facts:

• New synthetic microfiber panel on medial side for enhanced abrasion resistance and improved feeling when in contact with the bike.

• New TPU shifter for increased protection on lower medial side.

• New TPU shin plate has been redesigned for greater impact absorption performance, thus improving abrasion resistance in a key area.

• New replaceable shin slider for additional abrasion resistance.

• New TPU stretch panel design with zip for an easier entry and exit and a closer, more optimized fit.

• Main upper material constructed using microfiber for optimum abrasion resistance, while also delivering high levels of flexibility.

• New front flex area for improved impact abrasion while also ensuring the natural front and back.

• New front flex area increases ventilation and airflow for additional breathability.

#ThinkingAhead #InnovatingAhead #AlpinestarsProtects #SupertechR #RacingAhead
